keyValuePair.Value: [PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] [WON MATCH] How would you evalutate your players' performance?
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] [WON MATCH] How would you evalutate your players' performance, given this comfortable win?
[PLACEHOLDER] [PRAISE - ATTACKERS] It was a spectacular win.

[PLACEHOLDER] [PRAISE - ATTACKERS] It was a spectacular win, and it's true we secured it with a comfortable margin. But now we have to focus on the final. We need to keep our heads in the game and be sure that we're comming home with that piece of silver.
[PLACEHOLDER] [MOTIVATE - DEFENDERS] Their performance was stellar
[PLACEHOLDER] [MOTIVATE - DEFENDERS] These boys managed a two goal win. Their performance was stellar and nothing less. I'm certain the lads will repeat this performance in the final, as well.
These boys managed a two goal win. Their performance was stellar and nothing less. I'm certain the lads will repeat this performance in the final, as well.
[PLACEHOLDER] [CALM - ALL] We need to focus on the final.
[PLACEHOLDER] [CALM - ALL] Indeed, this was a comfortable win. But now we have to focus on the final. We have some time to prepare and a few matches to test things out.
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] [WON MATCH] What was the deciding factor of this win?
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] [WON MATCH] You secured a close call win, with only one goal. In your opinion, what was the deciding factor?
You secured a close call win, with only one goal. In your opinion, what was the deciding factor?
[PLACEHOLDER] [PRAISE - ATTACKERS] We dominated.
[PLACEHOLDER] [PRAISE - ATTACKERS] We dominated the match and won. That's all that matters. Now we have the chance to recreate the same performance in the final against %1s.
[PLACEHOLDER] [MOTIVATE - DEFENDERS] My lads trained hard.

[PLACEHOLDER] [MOTIVATE - DEFENDERS] My lads trained hard and gave everything on that pitch today. Not only did we deserve this win, we showed that we needed it. We're headed to the final with the same mindset.
[PLACEHOLDER] [CALM - ALL] Strategy and experience.
[PLACEHOLDER] [CALM - ALL] Strategy and experience. That's our recipe. And given that we're in the finals now, it works.
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] [WON MATCH] What do you think made this win possible?
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] [WON MATCH] Congratulations on this amazing win! What do you think made it possible?
[PLACEHOLDER] [PRAISE - MIDFIELDERS AND SYMPATHIZE DEFENDERS] Hard training and teamwork.

[PLACEHOLDER] [PRAISE - MIDFIELDERS AND SYMPATHIZE DEFENDERS] Hard training and teamwork, made such a win possible. So many goals in a %1s semi-final is not possible with only solo plays. We will surely repeat this performance in the final.
[PLACEHOLDER] [MOTIVATE - ATTACKERS AND PRAISE - DEFENDERS] Superior force!

[PLACEHOLDER] [MOTIVATE - ATTACKERS AND PRAISE - DEFENDERS] Our superior force made it possible! We played fantastically and the score shows it. I assume at some point, %1s just lost the will to fight.
Our superior force made it possible! We played fantastically and the score shows it. I assume at some point, %1s just lost the will to fight.
[PLACEHOLDER] [CALM - ALL] A sensational win.
[PLACEHOLDER] [CALM - ALL] These lads managed a sensational win with a 3 goal lead, in a %1s semi-final match. Let that sink in for a second.
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] [LOST MATCH] Do you think you could've played better?
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] [LOST MATCH] Do you think you could've played better? What do you think you could've done different?
[PLACEHOLDER] [CALM - ALL] Next year we will prepare more and perform better.
[PLACEHOLDER] [CALM - ALL] The lads played well, in my opinion. Clearly, this time %1s was the better team. Next year we will prepare more and perform better.
[PLACEHOLDER] [SYMPATHIZE - DEFENDERS] No, we couldn't have.
[PLACEHOLDER] [SYMPATHIZE - DEFENDERS] No, we couldn't have. The players gave it their best shot but it was not enough. We got this far and lost.
[PLACEHOLDER] [CRITICIZE- MIDFIELDERS] We will train more.
[PLACEHOLDER] [CRITICIZE- MIDFIELDERS] We will train more and come better prepared next year.
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] [LOST MATCH] Are you going to make any major changes in your squad?
[PLACEHOLDER QUESTION] [LOST MATCH] Given the crushing defeat you suffered today, and the cup elimination, are you going to make any major changes in your squad?
[PLACEHOLDER] [CALM - ALL] I understand the pressure.
I understand the pressure.
[PLACEHOLDER] [CALM - ALL] No. I completely understand the stress the lads have been put through and thoroughly respect their efforts. No changes will be made
No. I completely understand the stress the lads have been put through and thoroughly respect their efforts. No changes will be made
[PLACEHOLDER] [SYMPATHIZE - ATTACKERS AND CRITICIZE - MIDFIELDERS] We have to.
[PLACEHOLDER] [SYMPATHIZE - ATTACKERS AND CRITICIZE - MIDFIELDERS] It is clear the current strategy isn't working out for us. We clearly need to change something.
[PLACEHOLDER] [CRITICIZE- DEFENDERS AND MOTIVATE - MIDFIELDERS] Let's not rush to any conclusions.
[PLACEHOLDER] [CRITICIZE- DEFENDERS AND MOTIVATE - MIDFIELDERS] I wouldn't rush to any conclusions. We need to examine any issues and find a proper solution.
